Package org.jlab.phaser.model

Class ResultFilter

java.lang.Object
org.jlab.phaser.model.ResultFilter
public final class ResultFilter extends Object
An immutable result query filter.

Individual filter parameters are ignored if null. The parameters which are not null are combined with SQL "and".
